# Puchi Frontend

Puchi là nền tảng web học tiếng Việt. Frontend dùng **Next.js 16 (App Router) + React 19**.

## Tech Stack

| Thành phần | Công nghệ |
|------------|-----------|
| Framework | Next.js 16 (App Router, output: standalone) |
| UI | Tailwind CSS v4 + Shadcn UI (New York) |
| State | Zustand v5 |
| Auth | Auth-service (self-hosted) — custom AuthProvider + in-memory token + HttpOnly cookie SSR |
| i18n | next-intl (9 ngôn ngữ) |
| Animation | Motion + Rive |
| Runtime | Bun (install) + Node.js 22 (build & run) |

## Auth — Auth-service (self-hosted, xoá Zitadel)

**Đã migrate từ Zitadel → Auth-service tự xây dựng (Go/Kratos).** Token model:

| Token | Lưu ở đâu | TTL | Mục đích |
|-------|-----------|-----|----------|
| access_token (JWT RS256) | **In-memory** (React state) + HttpOnly cookie (SSR) | 15 phút | Auth header cho backend API |
| refresh_token (opaque) | **HttpOnly cookie** (domain api.puchi.io.vn, Path=/auth) | 30 ngày | Refresh access token |

### Auth flow tổng thể

```
1. LOGIN:
   Browser → POST api.puchi.io.vn/auth/login
   ← Response body: { access_token, expires_in, user }
   ← Set-Cookie: refresh_token (HttpOnly, Secure, SameSite=None, Path=/auth)
   → Lưu access_token in-memory (React state, token-manager.ts)
   → POST /api/auth/set-session → set HttpOnly access_token cookie (puchi.io.vn)

2. CLIENT API CALL:
   fetchWithAuth("/v1/profile")
   → Đọc access_token in-memory
   → Gắn Authorization: Bearer <token>
   → Gọi api.puchi.io.vn/v1/profile
   401 → POST /auth/refresh (refresh_token cookie tự gửi) → retry

3. PAGE RELOAD:
   Browser → proxy.ts (check session_active cookie, puchi.io.vn)
   → AuthProvider mount → GET /api/auth/restore-session → restore in-memory token
   → GET /api/auth/sessions (Bearer) → verify session

4. SERVER-SIDE (Server Components / Server Actions):
   backendFetch() → đọc access_token từ HttpOnly cookie (set bởi set-session)
   → Gắn Authorization: Bearer <token> → gọi backend service
```

### Custom AuthProvider

```typescript
// src/providers/AuthProvider.tsx
const auth = useAuth()
auth.login(email, password)    // POST /api/auth/login → in-memory token + sync SSR cookie
auth.register(email, password) // POST /api/auth/register
auth.logout()                  // POST /api/auth/logout → clear in-memory + clear SSR cookie
```

### Token Manager (in-memory singleton)

```typescript
// src/lib/token-manager.ts
getToken()          // Đọc in-memory token
setToken(token)     // Lưu in-memory
clearToken()        // Xoá in-memory
tryRefreshToken()   // POST /auth/refresh (dùng HttpOnly refresh_token cookie)
syncTokenToCookie() // POST /api/auth/set-session → đồng bộ lên HttpOnly cookie SSR
```

### Fetch wrapper (tự động Bearer + auto-refresh)

```typescript
// src/lib/fetch-with-auth.ts
fetchWithAuth<T>(url, options)     // Throw on error
fetchWithAuthResult<T>(url, options) // { ok, data } | { ok, error }

// src/lib/client-api.ts — dùng fetchWithAuth bên trong
clientFetch<T>(path, options)
```

### SSR Cookie Route Handlers

| Route | Mô tả |
|-------|-------|
| `POST /api/auth/set-session` | Set HttpOnly `access_token` + `session_active` cookies (puchi.io.vn) |
| `GET /api/auth/restore-session` | Đọc `access_token` từ HttpOnly cookie → trả về client |
| `POST /api/auth/clear-session` | Clear cả 2 cookies |

### Proxy (middleware.ts)

Check `session_active` cookie (puchi.io.vn domain) — không phải `refresh_token` (api.puchi.io.vn, không đọc được từ puchi.io.vn).

### Endpoints (frontend gọi tới api.puchi.io.vn/auth/)

| Method | Path | Auth required | Mô tả |
|--------|------|:---:|-------|
| POST | `/auth/login` | No | Login → trả về access_token + set refresh_token cookie |
| POST | `/auth/register` | No | Register |
| POST | `/auth/refresh` | Cookie | Refresh token (dùng HttpOnly refresh_token cookie) |
| POST | `/auth/logout` | Bearer | Logout (revoke session + clear cookie) |
| GET | `/auth/sessions` | Bearer | List sessions |
| DELETE | `/auth/sessions/{id}` | Bearer | Revoke session |
| GET | `/auth/social/{provider}` | No | OAuth2 redirect |
| POST | `/auth/magic-link/send` | No | Magic link (NATS → email) |
| PUT | `/auth/password/change` | Bearer | Change password |
| POST | `/auth/password/reset/request` | No | Request password reset |
| PUT | `/auth/password/reset` | No | Complete password reset |

## Docker Build

Multi-stage build với Bun + Node.js:

| Stage | Image | Purpose |
|-------|-------|---------|
| deps | `oven/bun:1.2-slim` | Install dependencies |
| builder | `node:22-alpine` | Build Next.js |
| runner | `node:22-alpine` | Run production (non-root user nextjs) |

Build args từ CI/CD:
- `NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL` — https://puchi.io.vn
- `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` — https://api.puchi.io.vn

## CI/CD

GitHub Actions (`ci-cd.yml`):
- **Lint**: Bun install → ESLint
- **Build & Push**: Docker login GHCR → Build + Push (tag: latest + sha)
- **Build args**: NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL, NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL, NEXT_PUBLIC_WEBSITE_DOMAIN
- **Registry**: `ghcr.io/puchidemy/puchi-frontend`

## Key Env Vars

| Env | Production value | Notes |
|-----|-----------------|-------|
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL` | `https://puchi.io.vn` | App domain |
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` | `https://api.puchi.io.vn` | API gateway (dùng chung cho auth + backend) |

## Scripts

```bash
bun install          # Cài dependencies (dùng bun.lock)
bun run dev          # Dev server
bun run build        # Build production (chạy bằng Node.js)
bun run start        # Start production
bun run lint         # ESLint
```

## Cấu trúc thư mục

```
src/
├── app/[locale]/         # Next.js App Router pages (i18n)
├── app/api/auth/         # Route Handlers: set-session, restore-session, clear-session
├── components/           # UI components (Shadcn + custom)
│   └── auth/             # AuthCard, SignInForm, SignUpForm, SocialLoginButtons
├── actions/              # Server Actions (logoutAction, profiles, social)
├── lib/                  # Core utilities
│   ├── token-manager.ts  # In-memory token + auto-refresh
│   ├── fetch-with-auth.ts# Bearer wrapper + 401 interceptor
│   ├── client-api.ts     # Client-side fetch (useAuth-optional)
│   ├── api-contracts.ts  # API type contracts
│   └── backend.ts        # Server-side fetch (SSR)
├── providers/            # AuthProvider (useAuth hook)
├── store/                # Zustand stores
├── hooks/                # Custom hooks
├── i18n/                 # Translation config
├── styles/               # Global styles
├── constants/            # Constants
├── config/               # env.ts (Zod-validated env config)
├── proxy.ts              # Middleware (xác thực bằng session_active cookie)
└── types/                # TypeScript types
```

## Kết nối Backend

- API: `api.puchi.io.vn` qua Envoy Gateway (dùng `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL`)
- Auth: gọi thẳng `api.puchi.io.vn/auth/*` (auth-service)
- Server-side fetch: đọc `access_token` từ HttpOnly cookie (set bởi `/api/auth/set-session`), gắn `Authorization: Bearer`
- Client-side fetch: `fetchWithAuth()` — Bearer từ in-memory token + auto-refresh khi 401
